   <concept id="GSAM_505_403" class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
      <title class="- topic/title "> 
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">505.403</ph> 
         <ph rev="Change 193 December 6, 2024" class="- topic/ph ">Requests from members of Congress.</ph>
      </title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d126e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d124e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>  The contracting officer shall consult with legal counsel if the response would disclose any of the following:</p>
					          <ol id="d126e23" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d124e27" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>  Classified material.</p>
						            </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d124e36" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>  Confidential business information.</p>
						            </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d124e45" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph> Contractor bid or proposal information or source selection information as defined in FAR 3.104-3.</p>
						            </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d124e54" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>  Information prejudicial to a competitive acquisition.</p>
						            </li>
               </ol>
				        </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d124e74" class="- topic/p " rev="Change 193 December 6, 2024"> 
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>  Refer the proposed response to the HCA and inform the OCIA of the action taken.</p>
				        </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
